<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A Thuok ie Lal Isu'n</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa'n ei hehpihna chu.
 Van sana khawlai taihsan in;
 Gilo chate ei hawl di'n.
 A thuok ie, Lal Isu'n.

[V2]
 Lungkhamna thing kraws chu kei din a pua,
 Chau in a puk hi!
 Kilhna thik khet kei di'n ana taluoi.
 Aw ka gen thei puoi.

[V3]
 2. Chenna khak loh gam tawh chu,
 Puon san silh a ling phek chu khun;
 Gimtheih tincheng thuok zo in,
 Belam No Lal Isu.

[V4]
 3. Etchim theih loh Lal Isu.
 Mi gilo di'n a Kraws chu pun;
 Kalvari lam zuon dingin,
 A gimthei ie ka Lal.

[V5]
 4. Aw, kei dinga thuok zo in,
 Kalvari tang thing kraws chungah;
 Ka gitloh cheng puo kawmin,
 Ei tan tai Lal Isu'n.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>51</hymn_number>
</song>